title: Turak, Iran
text: Turak (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Tūraḵ) is a village in <a href="Chelo%20Rural%20District">Chelo Rural District</a>, <a href="Chelo%20District">Chelo District</a>, <a href="Andika%20County">Andika County</a>, <a href="Khuzestan%20Province">Khuzestan Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 66, in 14 families.
